WEBVTT

00:02.896 --> 00:06.031
Adrian's not pregnant.
I saw the results,
and they were wrong.

00:06.032 --> 00:08.467
The tests are accurate.
Well, maybe Adrian
read it wrong.

00:08.468 --> 00:10.436
Maybe she's not pregnant
because she had an abortion.

00:10.437 --> 00:12.638
I told her not to do that,
and I don't think
she would do that.

00:12.639 --> 00:14.340
If my parents think
I have a place to live,

00:14.341 --> 00:16.775
then my dad can accept the job,
and they'll take off.

00:16.776 --> 00:18.143
Where are you
really gonna stay?

00:18.144 --> 00:19.478
I don't know.
I'll find someplace.

00:19.479 --> 00:22.481
You, Amy Juergens,
have been invited to attend

00:22.482 --> 00:25.918
a four-week, all-expenses paid
program for young musicians

00:25.919 --> 00:27.386
this summer in New York.

00:27.387 --> 00:29.221
Congratulations
on getting the offer,

00:29.222 --> 00:31.590
and my condolences on not
being able to accept.

00:31.591 --> 00:33.325
If people find out
that I was pregnant,

00:33.326 --> 00:35.628
or later,
find out that I had an abortion,

00:35.629 --> 00:37.062
I can live with that.

00:37.063 --> 00:40.299
I'm gonna tell my mother.
My mother will go with me.

00:40.300 --> 00:42.134
Ben, Adrian is pregnant.

00:42.135 --> 00:45.137
- No, she's not.
- Yes, she is.

00:45.138 --> 00:47.106
And if she told you she isn't,
she lied.

00:47.107 --> 00:49.108
I got accepted
into a summer program

00:49.109 --> 00:51.610
at the Nomkomf School
of Music in New York.
You should go.

00:51.611 --> 00:54.046
Ben, whatever it is,
you can tell me.

00:54.047 --> 00:56.649
I'm your dad.
I love you.

00:56.650 --> 00:59.785
Adrian's pregnant,
and it's my baby.

